Package: labelmanagerpnp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, usb-modeswitch, usb-modeswitch-data
Description: Web interface for Dymo LabelManager PnP label printers
 Rust-native single-binary web interface for Dymo LabelManager PnP
 and compatible D1-tape label printers. Provides a pixel editor and
 text rendering mode accessible from any browser on the local network.
 .
 Features: direct USB printing via nusb, cosmic-text font rendering,
 REST API, embedded static assets, configurable label definitions.
